'''斯蒂芬·沃伦·博斯沃思'''（{{lang-en|Stephen Warren Bosworth}}；{{bd|1939年|12月4日|2016年|1月4日|catIdx=S}}），是[[美国|美国]]的学者、外交官。曾担任“美日财团”主席、美国驻[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]大使、美国驻[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]大使、美国驻[[韩国|韩国]]大使、[[朝鲜|朝鲜]]问题特使。<ref>[https://sais.jhu.edu/news-press/stephen-bosworth-1939-2016 Stephen Bosworth, 1939-2016 | Johns Hopkins SAIS]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.38north.org/tag/stephen-bosworth/ |title=stephen bosworth Archives {{!}} 38 North |access-date=2020-12-06 |archive-date=2019-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190722201418/https://www.38north.org/tag/stephen-bosworth/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/secretary/remarks/2016/01/250979.htm |title=On the Passing of Ambassador Stephen Bosworth |access-date=2020-12-06 |archive-date=2021-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323145736/https://2009-2017.state.gov/secretary/remarks/2016/01/250979.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://www.japantimes.co.jp/tag/stephen-bosworth/ Stephen Bosworth - The Japan Times]</ref>

